  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/32aa1a1907217044c28002f3a5b51e11.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=83 /></span><br><br><u><strong>You can provide valuable comments and suggestions in steam community, or any ideas email to <a href=\"mailto:AnotherKnifeGames@gmail.com\">AnotherKnifeGames@gmail.com</a>. I hope you also participate in the development process!</strong></u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn the Fundamentals Of Digital Circuits</h2>You can master the rules of digital circuits through this game, and the difficulty of the levels is progressive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/189a1870f6c1429cf0f5d53bfcccb3ae.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=291 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete the Level With Limited Components</h2>Each level is very challenging, sometimes the difficulty is increased by limiting the use of electronic components.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/49f3300356daabf613381bee46233ea7.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=420 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write Code, and Build Circuits that Carry Program Functionality</h2>Later levels will unlock CPU usage, allowing you to write code to solve more complex problems.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/393a3161c16dbde7e0e8e805d7d3103e.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=540 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/32aa1a1907217044c28002f3a5b51e11.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=83 /></span><br><br><u><strong>You can provide valuable comments and suggestions in steam community, or any ideas email to <a href=\"mailto:AnotherKnifeGames@gmail.com\">AnotherKnifeGames@gmail.com</a>. I hope you also participate in the development process!</strong></u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn the Fundamentals Of Digital Circuits</h2>You can master the rules of digital circuits through this game, and the difficulty of the levels is progressive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/189a1870f6c1429cf0f5d53bfcccb3ae.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=291 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete the Level With Limited Components</h2>Each level is very challenging, sometimes the difficulty is increased by limiting the use of electronic components.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/49f3300356daabf613381bee46233ea7.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=420 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write Code, and Build Circuits that Carry Program Functionality</h2>Later levels will unlock CPU usage, allowing you to write code to solve more complex problems.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287030/extras/393a3161c16dbde7e0e8e805d7d3103e.avif?t=1676439881\" width=600 height=540 /></span>",
